snippet.title: Roboquest | Official Gameplay Trailer (2020)
snippet.description:
As of 20th August, we’ll be in Early Access.

Wishlist Roboquest on Steam:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/692890/Roboquest/
 
Roboquest is a fast FPS Roguelite in a scorched futureworld. You're a rebooted Guardian, ready to kick some metal ass! Fight with your buddy or by yourself and annihilate hordes of deadly bots in ever-changing environments.
 
Soundtrack: ‘Modify Me’ and 'Connect' by Noisecream. Check him out: https://open.spotify.com/artist/2EiUFCnwVBJ11bHlbwBypw
